  "title": "Commercial Banking RM",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Our Client</strong></u><br />Financial Services Company<br /><br /><u><strong>Location</strong></u><br />West<br /><br />Job Description & Requirements</p><p>As a <strong>Relationship Manager</strong>, you will be responsible for promoting and selling various types of loans to commercial clients. You will be involved in conducting basic credit analysis.<br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Customer Acquisition & Retention</strong>: Engage with prospective and existing clients to introduce banking products and services tailored to their financial needs.</li><li><strong>Cold-calling:</strong> Proactively reach out to potential customers to introduce our products and services.</li><li><strong>Relationship Building</strong>: Develop and nurture long-term relationships with clients, ensuring high satisfaction and continued loyalty to the bank.</li><li><strong>Cross-Selling</strong>: Identify opportunities for cross-selling additional products and services to existing customers.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree with at least 2 years of experience in selling mortgages or loans.</li><li>Confident communicator who enjoys speaking to people from all walks of life.</li><li>Eager to learn and adaptable in a fast-paced environment.</li></ul><p><strong>Why Join Our Client?</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Competitive Salary & Commission Structure</strong>: Enjoy a competitive base salary with performance-based incentives.</li><li><strong>Career Development</strong>: Opportunities for growth within the organisation as part of a dynamic team.</li><li><strong>Comprehensive Benefits Package</strong>: Health, dental, paid time off etc.</li><li><strong>Great Team Culture</strong>: Supportive, energetic and inclusive environment.</li></ul><p>If you’re passionate about sales and building strong customer relationships, we want to hear from you! Click on the “Apply” button to send us your resume.<br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br /></p><p>EA Reg No: R1329095 (Canice Sar)<br />EA License No: 21C0434</p>",
